title: Stocks to watch on Wednesday
text:
Wed, Sep 2, 2015, 8:01 AM AEST - Australia Markets open in 1 hr 59 mins Stocks to watch on Wednesday AAP â€“ 10 minutes ago 
Stocks to watch on the Australian stock exchange on Wednesday, Sept 2: 
BHP - BHP BILLITON 
OSH - OIL SEARCH 
WPL - WOODSIDE PETROLEUM 
Oil prices tumble overnight after Chinese manufacturing data further indicated a slowdown in the world's second largest economy and shook market confidence. 
FMG - FORTESCUE METALS 
The iron ore price lifts slightly overnight, rising US38 cents to $US56.59. @y7finance on Twitter, become a fan on Facebook Terms
